## Integration

- **Obsidian**: `templates/obsidian/` → vault `05-Agents/`
- **Sub-agent**: writes `sub_stop.json`, never reports PASS without artifacts
- **JIRA**: add `ops/jira_post.py` per project (not included in stub)
